{"tid":2029864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁愛詩：引入內地國安法不適當","createTime":"2020-05-22T12:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T08:42:20.000Z","uid":297241,"like":4,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"37ac9016eb94d8ffe6e6e0ed099afd50c8fdd71e","tid":2029864,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:42:30.000Z","msg":"梁愛詩：引入內地國安法不適當<br />\n<br />\n【now新聞台】基本法委員會副主任梁愛詩指，內地國家安全法與基本法23條性質不同，國安法難以適用於本港的法律制度，引入內地國安法並不適當。"},{"pid":"2622f1c91828768aa6a3619d1369884752421d84","tid":2029864,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:42:56.000Z","msg":"驚阿？"},{"pid":"0977f2b88a37bc1418b1448302288581e3f705d2","tid":2029864,"uid":76063,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:43:28.000Z","msg":"叛國-&gt;拉得"},{"pid":"bdd4a09af6c703757352b6b85faf0e23d76c0d8f","tid":2029864,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:44:08.000Z","msg":"反了?"},{"pid":"91087a94edd9b12a4b58916c5b53671ae7cfcf25","tid":2029864,"uid":57543,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:44:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>21 Jan 2015</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>block</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"2a222e7d4e3b3426785b8c9bff750844a2414bca","tid":2029864,"uid":103693,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:44:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=123747&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D123747%26refer%3D&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSvhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=ca67466a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D123747%26refer%3D&h=812e48de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=123747&amp;refer=</a><br />\n2015/01/21"},{"pid":"8b87fe640c86f6f40cd5d88151237b241420affb","tid":2029864,"uid":133609,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0977f2b88a37bc1418b1448302288581e3f705d2","tid":2029864,"uid":76063,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:43:28.000Z","msg":"叛國-&gt;拉得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:45:10.000Z","msg":"佢意思係港版國安法就無問題"},{"pid":"463e8d96781d5276880aa9bdbf7701345a2757bf","tid":2029864,"uid":19218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:46:37.000Z","msg":"收撚皮啦白髮魔女"},{"pid":"a9e29d4f56813b5e7ae40d2e3ef496479bed0866","tid":2029864,"uid":155012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"91087a94edd9b12a4b58916c5b53671ae7cfcf25","tid":2029864,"uid":57543,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:44:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>21 Jan 2015</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>block</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a241e6ef830b62b173f91db172fe80a715f74c","tid":2029864,"uid":197563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:56:10.000Z","msg":"鞭"},{"pid":"9d2bc01dbf65e2743b32210ebea05d5efc8cf4ee","tid":2029864,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:00:24.000Z","msg":"質疑國家算唔算顛覆國家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e97192361577230a39a1327ea7907b548b09e4","tid":2029864,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:00:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位：黑色五毛風向警告，大量五毛正在吹襲連登</span></strong><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下強行通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span>"},{"pid":"5bb14e784f1bcba7db7e05ed7e34b15129c0ebc6","tid":2029864,"uid":297241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:01:08.000Z","msg":"梁愛詩：國安法不會在港實施<br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會1日通過國家安全法，首次有提及港澳的條文。社會關注港人日後一些行為，返內地時會否被定罪。對此，香港基本法委員會副主任梁愛詩表示，全國人大常委會法工委副主任鄭淑娜已作出交代，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法不會在香港實施</span>，因為這並不列於香港基本法附件三內：「國安法只屬框架性法律，即使國安法要在香港實施，也不可直接實施，何況香港基本法第廿三條已有相關的條文，規定香港應自行就國家安全問題立法。」"},{"pid":"193b8ec68109a6589543ab758660d41b150975ec","tid":2029864,"uid":124667,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5bb14e784f1bcba7db7e05ed7e34b15129c0ebc6","tid":2029864,"uid":297241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:01:08.000Z","msg":"梁愛詩：國安法不會在港實施<br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會1日通過國家安全法，首次有提及港澳的條文。社會關注港人日後一些行為，返內地時會否被定罪。對此，香港基本法委員會副主任梁愛詩表示，全國人大常委會法工委副主任鄭淑娜已作出交代，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法不會在香港實施</span>，因為這並不列於香港基本法附件三內：「國安法只屬框架性法律，即使國安法要在香港實施，也不可直接實施，何況香港基本法第廿三條已有相關的條文，規定香港應自行就國家安全問題立法。」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:03:15.000Z","msg":"燒山好似有講"},{"pid":"8b576f2b8917c129f569dfb466ad1f77f6116f2a","tid":2029864,"uid":3357,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:04:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc41426c42bf2a774d6ba07337